#import "theme.typ": *
#import "diagrams.typ": *

#chapter-page("06", "介词短语与高频搭配", "Phrasal Prepositions & Collocations", color: c-accent)

英语里还有多词介词表达，以及动词、形容词、名词与介词形成的搭配。准确使用这些关系有助于 IELTS 写作，但分数来自表达精确和连贯，而不是堆叠“高级短语”。

#principle[
  多词介词表达由多个词共同引出补语，例如 #en[because of rain]、#en[in terms of cost]。不同语法体系对部分表达的分类可能不同，本章以学习功能为主。\

  例:#hl[because of] + rain = because of rain (因为下雨)
]

== 基础：先看介词后面能接什么

#table(
  columns: (1.8cm, 1fr, 1fr),
  align: (center + horizon, left, left),
  stroke: 0.5pt + c-line,
  inset: 7pt,
  table.header(
    table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*补语形式*],
    table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*例子*],
    table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*提醒*],
  ),
  [名词短语], [after the meeting / with great care], [最常见形式],
  [代词宾格], [between you and me / with her], [不用 I / she 等主格],
  [-ing 形式], [before leaving / interested in learning], [介词后不直接接动词原形],
  [从句], [after we left / since he arrived], [传统教材常把此类词另称连词；学习时关注后接结构],
)

#warn(title: "to 的两种身份")[
  #example((
    [look forward #hl[to] meeting you —— #en[to] 是介词，后接 #en[-ing]],
    [want #hl[to] meet you —— #en[to] 是不定式标记，后接动词原形],
  ))
]

#tip[
  #en[because of] 后接名词短语：#en[because of the rain]；#en[because] 后接从句：#en[because it was raining]。
]

== 一、原因 / 结果类

#table(
  columns: (1fr, 1fr),
  align: (left, left),
  stroke: 0.5pt + c-line,
  inset: 7pt,
  table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*短语*],
  table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*例句*],
  [#hl[because of] (因为)],
  [The match was cancelled #hl[because of] rain.],
  [#hl[due to] (由于 — 正式)],
  [The delay was #hl[due to] bad weather.],
  [#hl[owing to] (由于 — 正式)],
  [#hl[Owing to] the strike, trains are delayed.],
  [#hl[on account of] (因为)],
  [He retired #hl[on account of] poor health.],
  [#hl[as a result of] (作为……的结果)],
  [Many died #hl[as a result of] the earthquake.],
  [#hl[thanks to] (由于/多亏；常带正面或讽刺语气)],
  [#hl[Thanks to] you, we succeeded.],
  [#hl[for the sake of] (为了……起见)],
  [Stop arguing #hl[for the sake of] the kids.],
)

#warn(title: "due to vs because of")[
  现代英语中两者都可引出原因，但搭配和语域略有不同：
  #example((
    [He stayed home #hl[because of] illness. (中性、适用范围广)],
    [The delay was #hl[due to] bad weather. (常见于表语位置和较正式语境)],
    [#hl[Due to] bad weather, the flight was cancelled. (现代正式英语中也常作句首原因状语)],
  ))
  IELTS 写作不必遵守“#en[due to] 只能修饰名词”的旧式禁令；更重要的是避免反复使用同一连接方式。
]

== 二、关于 / 论述类（IELTS 写作常见）

#table(
  columns: (1fr, 1fr),
  align: (left, left),
  stroke: 0.5pt + c-line,
  inset: 7pt,
  table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*短语*],
  table.cell(fill: c-soft2)[*例句*],
  [#hl[with regard to] (关于 — 正式)],
  [#hl[With regard to] your letter, we will reply by Friday.],
  [#hl[in terms of] (就……而言)],
  [#hl[In terms of] cost, option A is better.],
  [#hl[in relation to] (关于/与……相比)],
  [This is small #hl[in relation to] the total.],
  [#hl[as for] (至于)],
  [#hl[As for] the cost, it remains a concern.],
  [#hl[when it comes to] (谈到)],
  [#hl[When it comes to] music, she's an expert.],
  [#hl[on the subject of] (关于)],
  [a book #hl[on the subject of] AI],
)

#tip[
  语域提示:
  - 用 #hl[in terms of] 表"从某角度看"
  - #hl[when it comes to] 较口语化，正式写作中不要反复使用
  - #hl[with regard to] 适合明确转换论述对象，不应代替真正的逻辑衔接
]

