== 六、IELTS 写作常用名词搭配

名词后的介词既受意义关系影响，也有惯例化搭配。先理解“对象、幅度、影响目标”等角色，再用完整句块巩固。

=== 趋势/数据类 (Task 1)
#example((
  [an increase #hl[in] prices (价格 #cn-hl[的] 上升 —— in 接对象)],
  [a rise #hl[of] 10% (#cn-hl[幅度] —— of 接数字)],
  [a fall #hl[in] demand / a drop #hl[of] 20%],
  [a change #hl[in] the system / a difference #hl[between] A and B],
  [a correlation #hl[between] X and Y],
))

#principle(title: "黄金区分:in vs of")[
  - #hl[in] + #cn-hl[被描述对象] (prices, demand, sales)
  - #hl[of] + #cn-hl[数量/幅度] (10%, a third, 50 dollars)
  #formula[in = "什么的"; of = "多少的"]
]

=== 态度/评价类 (Task 2)
#example((
  [a reason #hl[for] (……的理由)],
  [a solution #hl[to] (……的解决办法)],
  [an effect / impact #hl[on] (对……的影响)],
  [a demand #hl[for] / a need #hl[for] (对……的需求)],
  [an advantage #hl[of] / a disadvantage #hl[of] (……的优/缺点)],
  [the cause #hl[of] (……的原因)],
  [the importance #hl[of] (……的重要性)],
))

#tip(title: "同一个名词，介词改变关系")[
  名词并不总是只绑定一个介词。先问后面的成分扮演什么角色：
  #example((
    [the advantage #hl[of] online learning (某事物本身的优点)],
    [an advantage #hl[over] traditional classes (相对于另一方的优势)],
    [an advantage #hl[to] small businesses (对某群体的益处)],
    [a difference #hl[between] the two plans (比较双方) / a difference #hl[in] cost (差异所在的维度)],
    [the reason #hl[for] the delay (直接说明原因) / the reason #hl[behind] the decision (强调背后的动机)],
  ))
]

